@aiatmeta releases real-time artificial intelligence language translation model: Seamless

This model consolidates the previous three Seamless series models and can translate over 100 languages in real time, with a delay of less than 2 seconds, starting the translation while the speaker is still speaking.

Seamless translation not only involves textual conversion but also maintains the speaker's emotions, tone, and intonation, making the translated speech more natural and authentic.
